    • ChefManager

      public ChefManager(float chefScale, UIOverlay overlay, com.badlogic.gdx.physics.box2d.World world, KeyboardInput keyboardInput)
      Parameters:
      chefScale - the amount to scale the texture by so that each chef is an accurate size.
      overlay - the user interface overlay to display information about the current chef and time, and to provide more controls.
      world - Box2D world to use for Chef collision and movement.
      keyboardInput - Input processor for input from the keyboard. Passed down to the chefs this class owns.
